title: Heavy.Weather.Presents-4.Musical.Acts.HDTV.x264-CLDD
description:
"Heavy Weather Presents" consists of 4 Musical Acts from around the province of Newfoundland & Labrador. There are no live audiences and everything is shot on location. While we are not set out to directly answer "why is there so much music from a place with so few people?" It is an underlying theme.



Featuring:


Steve Maloney and the Wondering Kind
Joanna Barker
Hear/Say
The Elizabeatans
